sparqlQuery: PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> select distinct ?uri where { ?uri dct:subject dbc:Former_British_colonies. ?uri dct:subject dbc:Thirteen_Colonies. }

languageToQuestion.en: What were the original 13 British colonies?
languageToQuestion.de: Was waren die Originalen 13 Britischen Kolonien?
languageToQuestion.it: Quali furono le 13 originarie colonie britanniche?
languageToQuestion.fr: Quelles étaient les 13 colonnies britanniques originales?

sparqlQuery: PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> select distinct ?date where { res:Paraguay dbp:establishedDate ?date . }

languageToQuestion.en: When did Paraguay proclaim its independence?
languageToQuestion.de: Wann hat Paraguay seine Unabhängigkeit verkündet?
languageToQuestion.it: Quando si dichiarò indipendente il Paraguay?
languageToQuestion.fr: Quand est-ce que le Paraguay a prononcé son indépendance?

sparqlQuery: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX dct: <http://purl.org/dc/terms/> PREFIX dbc: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/Category:> PREFIX dbp: <http://dbpedia.org/property/> select distinct ?uri where { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Person . ?uri dct:subject dbc:Presidents_of_the_United_States . ?uri dbp:termEnd ?termEnd . FILTER(year(NOW()) - year(?termEnd) <= 20) }

languageToQuestion.en: Give me all American presidents in the last 20 years.
languageToQuestion.de: Gib mir alle Amerikanischen Präsidenten der letzten 20 Jahre.
languageToQuestion.it: Dammi tutti i presidenti americani degli ultimi 20 anni.
languageToQuestion.fr: Donnez-moi le nom des présidents américains des 20 dernières années.

sparqlQuery: PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> select distinct ?uri where { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Holiday. }

languageToQuestion.en: Which holidays are celebrated around the world?
languageToQuestion.de: Welche Feiertage werden auf der Welt gefeiert?
languageToQuestion.it: Quali festività sono celebrate nel mondo?
languageToQuestion.fr: Quelles fêtes sont célébrées autour du monde?
